      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELEGANT CINDY (1) placed last time (20.10) at this track in a Other, finishing third and beaten 3.5 lengths. Expected to be in the finish. GOLDEN ZEAL (7) had been going along well winning a Other three back then placing at this track before missing the frame latest when fourth (23.17) at Murray Bridge. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break from out wide. Expected to do much better this time. BONMATI (4) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (20.14) last time in a Other at this track. Solid record at the distance winning four races. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Must be included in calculations. RUSSO (2) put a gap on his rivals last start. Must be respected.",
